{MUGEN CLIMB} Water/Darkness 3(You may summon this creature from your hand or graveyard by tapping 3 of your creatures and paying Water/Darkness 3.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ Whenever this creature attacks, your opponent reveals cards from the top of their deck until they reveal a spell. Your opponent puts that spell into their graveyard and then shuffles their deck. Cast that spell for no cost and put it into its owner's graveyard.

{MACH FIGHTER} (This creature can attack tapped or untapped creatures on the turn you put it.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature into the battle zone, you may choose one of your opponent's creatures and put it into its owner's mana zone. If you do, choose a non-evolution creature from your opponent's mana zone and put it into the battle zone.

{BLOCKER} (You may tap this creature to change the attack target of your opponent's creature to this creature.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature into the battle zone, you may put a non-evolution light creature that has "blocker" from your hand into the battle zone.

{VIVIDDRAW} {W5} (During your turn, when you draw this creature before you attack, you may reveal it. If you do, you may pay Water 5 to summon this creature this turn.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ Whenever this creature attacks, you may cast a spell that costs 9 or less from your hand or graveyard for no cost. If you do, after you cast that spell, put it on the bottom of your deck instead of your graveyard.

{BLOCKER} (You may tap this creature to change the attack target of your opponent's creature to this creature.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature into the battle zone, put 2 of your shields into your graveyard.

{BLOCKER} (You may tap this creature to change the attack target of your opponent's creature to this creature.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature into the battle zone, put a card from your mana zone on top of your deck.

{SPEED ATTACKER} (This creature doesn't get summoning sickness.)
{DOUBLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature, you may add all your shields to your hand. You can't use the "shield trigger" abilities.

